---
title: Honey-Soy Beef & Ramen Noodles with Roasted Cashews
description: Sometimes you can’t go past the classics, like this beef stir-fry with a sweet and savoury sauce. With thin ramen noodles and colourful veggies, it tastes like a takeaway delight, but with the satisfaction of making it yourself!
